collection.name: Space Doodles
collection.description:
Space Doodles are spaceships for your Doodle. Each Doodle in the original collection of 10,000 can launch their own personal spaceship that is generated from over 200 audio-visual traits and on-chain stats.

Your Space Doodle is your Doodle and selling it will allow the new purchaser to remove the Doodle from our secure smart contract. It is highly recommended that you launch and dock your Doodles directly from https://doodles.app
